Chair pads

So Comfortable, You Wouldn’t Want To Get Up!


Keep the conversations going as you sit comfortably at the dining table - thanks to our collection of chair pads! Check out the DJUPVIK cushion - it comes with removable covers that can be machine-washed so it’s easy to keep clean. Or for something for versatile, check out the reversible chair pads from ELSEBET series. One side patterned and one side plain - you can mix it up to create a theme with your dining table chairs or just flip all of them now and then to keep things exciting! And for ultimate comfort, check out the VIPPÄRT chair cushion - it has two identical sides so it can be turned over when one side gets worn out or dirty!
